title: What the US withdrawal from international bodies means for climate change and biodiversity
subhed: The US's exit from the United Nations Framework Convention on Climate Change, the Intergovernmental Panel on Climate Change and its equivalent for biodiversity threatens to further slow and hinder the fight against environmental crises.

title: Venezuela says in talks with US to restore diplomatic ties
subhed: The government of the South American country's interim President Delcy Rodriguez 'has decided to initiate an exploratory diplomatic process' with the US government, 'aimed at re-establishing diplomatic missions in both countries,' Foreign Minister Yvan Gil said in a statement.

title: The new luxury olive oils: 'Visitors come with the same curiosity as for wine'
subhed: Olive oil has gained a new status. Championed by Michelin-starred chefs, the ingredient is now treated with the same reverence as a fine vintage wine, reflecting a precious artisanal craft. A handful of French estates are distinguishing themselves, selling their extra virgin production at premium prices.
